Dear Steve, 
We're excited to host you at our Airbnb!
 
We do require all of our guests to complete pre-arrival form within 48h of booking through a secure link bellow.
 
http://app.chargeautomation.com/onlinecheckin?bookingid=951ed3d4-0f5f-4d45-a0d7-1b138f2e35a4&firstname=Steve‌

The information we collect will help us tailor your stay and is an essential part of our liability protection.‌

Looking forward to welcoming you!

Best regards, 
Martin

Hello Stephen,We are so excited for your arrival tomorrow on Sun, Sep 24 2023.

Address: 3728 20th Avenue SouthSt. Petersburg, FL 33711‌

Stay: Sun, Sep 24 2023 to Tue, Oct 31 2023‌

Check-In Time: 16:00

Check-out Time: 10:00‌

Wifi Network: MOTO1E46

Wifi Password: briefshirt329

DOOR CODE: 0545

Access Instructions:
Welcome to the Upscale 2 BR house you have reserved. The main blue part of the house is your destination. Please park in one or both of the two parking spots located in the driveway in front of the blue house. Please do not use the other separated parking in front of the white unit. Once you enter the house, you will find keys that can be used to unlock the gate leading to the laundry area. Please enjoy your stay, and don't hesitate to contact us if you need anything.

Now, before you arrive please take a look at our interactive Guidebook where you will find the house manual, local recommendations, and other details for your stay:https://hostful.ly/gbjktdd

If you have any questions, please reach out to us

Thank you for staying with us and safe travels,
Martin
